rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教訓囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b23d27920c72694e63674965a3ab7ec61c9697a","tid":109953,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係呀....冇還卡數幾過月就去到i?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一有past due就一定變i<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲左交一期都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n過幾日通常唔會有事<br />\n打去card ctr 講唔記得找跟住即刻找返通常冇事<br />\n亦唔會入tu<br />\n不過樓主差幾期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明顯係有意 呢d 一入tu 好難翻身<br />\n因為事實你真係欠過銀行幾期卡數<br />\n只不過係清左 但事實上你係欠過<br />\n冇架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教訓囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個教訓都幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c2547caca939090120bd784ebce71ac8e13ca8","tid":109953,"uid":75309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我之前有筆數欠了中銀幾個月，之後要求一筆清還。<br />\n整條數已經搞掂，請問目前我乜卡數都冇，信貸報告要甚麼時候才能有update?<br />\n利申 : 宜家評級為 I . 要向銀行或者其他信貸公司借錢結婚。</blockquote><br />\n好似成5年先清底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我過左4年仲係D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打，你有冇其他事務在身先，即係其他財務嘢，信用卡呀，供樓呀，等等"},{"pid":"82cd92f5a3efe42244276d448df7b2058d23d734","tid":109953,"uid":68903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>還完之後應該要1至2個月先更新記錄，借錢記錄可以用書面方式要求銀行整走<br />\n<br />\nTU i仔銀行仲肯借?</blockquote><br />\n巴打，more，please<br />\n冇喇，評級 i 宜家去申請，銀行肯定會揾環聯check，一睇就知道乜事，好難accept我申請。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環聯保留個人信貸資料的期限為多久？<br />\n<br />\n根據香港個人資料私隱專員公署頒布的《個人信貸資料實務守則》，保留期限如下：<br />\n<br />\n環聯可保留最新的信用卡和個人貸款帳戶紀錄，以作信貸參考之用。<br />\n由賬戶終止日期起開始計算，環聯可保留正常結束的信用卡和個人貸款帳戶紀錄5年。<br />\n由欠款金額全數償還日期起開始計算，環聯可保留逾期還款紀錄5年；或由欠款人根據香港個人資料私隱專員公署頒布的《個人信貸資料實務守則》通知環聯解除破產日期起計算，保留相關資料5年。兩者以最早的日期為準。<br />\n由法律程序日期起開始計算，環聯可保留破產申請紀錄8年，其他公眾紀錄7年。<br />\n由查詢日期起開始計算，環聯可保留會員查詢信貸報告的紀錄2年。<br />\n假如賬戶在結束前5年內未有出現超過60天的逾期欠款紀錄，而環聯收到會員通知，要求刪除該已結束賬戶的資料時，環聯會盡快將之從資料庫中刪除。"},{"pid":"5479f48b73a05d2694248474a658e5b4e2e4ff4b","tid":109953,"uid":2455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"借錢結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪害左個女仔啦"},{"pid":"6ea50295eaa8fd42e10412267e5798e6abdd2315","tid":109953,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"你呢個I 唔止遲還咁簡單<br />\n係咪重差緊卡數？ 同埋試過申請過P loan"},{"pid":"e73661084a1ed3b1b2975ee6756a9b35789534c6","tid":109953,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"借多幾單再準時還應該可以升返個tu"},{"pid":"542c3126d83fd738051e4070c1a91c663dc69b3c","tid":109953,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"956c7f8ed04f92a6af2e459fac4e1bf2ffefc36a","tid":109953,"uid":5919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"我想問 D係咪好難同銀行借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b21d25b3a86a18fa89b6f90bab478dfdb00d6f","tid":109953,"uid":75309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呢個I 唔止遲還咁簡單<br />\n係咪重差緊卡數？ 同埋試過申請過P loan</blockquote><br />\n冇任何卡數，之前清果筆就係私人貸款。"},{"pid":"75bd93054e66406f8ee96a7e4d906f435e7d8848","tid":109953,"uid":75309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借多幾單再準時還應該可以升返個tu</blockquote><br />\n咁嘅評級，借條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703e358444712fb18f2afe9a8028956706199e9a","tid":109953,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"TU 冇得急，一定要兩三個月先更新一次<br />\nTu I 銀行一定唔會借，巴打唔急的話咪keep 住用信用卡，準時還錢，慢慢等升級"},{"pid":"35474588ad6ef22c954c944b0219c4f1414d00ce","tid":109953,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:39:32.000Z","msg":"仆街一年前試過唔記得入錢 銀行半個月後打黎催 之後即刻入返 仲俾佢罰鳩左$500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪都會上tu留5年?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (準備買樓)"},{"pid":"134f4f4b5b27b0bb9f7615e7b04f9394651882dd","tid":109953,"uid":28201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T23:47:19.000Z","msg":"借題一問<br />\n之後係大眾借咗15萬 $4873/月 還36期 還咗9期<br />\n係恆生借50000 $2738.1/月 還24期 還咗5期<br />\n恆生卡數差40000<br />\n早排大眾打俾我話可以續借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家想借30000還咗卡數先唔知得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：tu h 月入17k 銀行過數出糧"},{"pid":"75d64ca89e4cd52adaef8243f9d8336002bd4525","tid":109953,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T23:48:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d786ed0f2594546859d3a57039139dc439051104","tid":109953,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T23:50:35.000Z","msg":"我遲卡數一日都有記錄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}